Error shapes also include validation errors in a 'details' array:

    {
        "detail": [
            {
                "loc": ["body", "start"],
                "msg": "field required",
                "type": "value_error.missing"
            },
            {
                "loc": ["body", "callback_url"],
                "msg": "field required",
                "type": "value_error.missing"
            }
        ]
    }

